              --- UnixDOOM - DOOM running in the Linux kernel ---               
                 Inspired by [https://github.com/NSG650/NtDOOM]                 

      Usage:
         [1] Build the project using the included makefile
         [2] Place a DOOM WAD file at [/DOOM/DOOM.WAD]
         [3] Load the kernel module with [insmod <path/to/UnixDOOM.ko>]
         [4] Unload the kernel module with [rmmod UnixDOOM]
